title: Algiers - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Algiers performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded March 27, 2023.

Songs:
Irreversible Damage
Out Of Style Tragedy
Cold World
Bite Back

Franklin Fisher - Keyboards / Guitar / Vocals
Ryan Mahan - Bass / Synth / Vocals
Lee Tesche - Guitar / Effects / Vocals
Matt Tong - Drums
Dante Foley - Drums

Host: Cheryl Waters
Audio Engineers: Evan Devine, Julian Martlew & Kevin Suggs
Audio Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Jim Beckmann
